title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Douglas DC6 - Install additional liveries
description:
In this how to we are going to look how you can install additional liveries for the Douglas DC6 aircraft. We will look at how you can install the additional liveries which are part of the default product and in addition look at the community liveries which are available for free at flightsim.to

The livery added from flightsim.to can be found on the link below:
https://flightsim.to/file/16648/pmdg-dc-6a-usaf-military-air-transport-service-07642
